    <sect3 role="installation">
      <title>Instalação de Xorg Fbdev Driver</title>

      <para>
        Install <application>Xorg Fbdev Driver</application> by running the
following commands:
      </para>

<screen><userinput>./configure $XORG_CONFIG &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

